    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Although the base forms of Karrnathi Undead are leagues above the near-mindless creatures raised by normal necromantic practices, they still lacked the imagination and intuition necessary to command themselves. Early on, living officers known as Bone Knights (as detailed in Rising) commanded the legions of Karrnathi undead, but production soon outstripped the capacity to train these knights.</p><p>Thus, the Blood of Vol priests developed the Dread Marshal, a type of Karrnathi undead possessed of a strong personality and force of will. These Dread Marshals were able to not only command their fellow Karrnathi undead, but to bolster their necromantic strength as well.</p>",
        "public": ""
      },
